{"tid":896903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[死神來了]  去年賭場槍擊案逃過死劫　27歲青年再遇槍擊送命","createTime":"2018-11-10T12:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T13:54:26.000Z","uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c733e67a55f7d92f28d8d04f3a55c339abbacd4a","tid":896903,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"美國加州一名槍手周三（7日）晚上闖入紹森歐克斯（Thousand Oaks）一間酒吧掃射，殺死最少12人，包括一名去年拉斯維加斯賭場音樂會槍擊案的倖存者。槍手其後自盡身亡。<br />\n<br />\n27歲的Telemachus Orfanos去年在拉斯維加斯賭場音樂會槍擊案中逃過死門關，但周三卻不幸再次遇到槍擊案並中槍身亡。死者母親表示，「我兒子和很多朋友在拉斯維加斯的那次，他回家了，但他昨晚（7日）沒有回家。我不需要祈禱，不需要想念，我要槍支管制。」Orfanos的父親則說，「特別諷刺的是，他（Orfanos）在現代歷史上最嚴重的大規模槍擊案中倖存後，卻在家鄉被殺。」<br />\n<br />\n於去年10月1日，拉斯維加斯一間賭場酒店舉行露天音樂會期間，一名槍手從酒店32樓亂槍掃射，擊斃58人。拉斯維加斯槍擊案的倖存者表示，他們近幾個月曾在紹森歐克斯的涉事酒吧聚會，本周槍擊案發生當日，他們亦在酒吧內。<br />\n<br />\n(英國廣播公司)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00005/1541822235852?fbclid=IwAR3nKg581IwT1jZn31gtsOJteY9i-G7X9tRwuAosSv2UOlhAR5CoeC_H1-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00005%2F1541822235852%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3nKg581IwT1jZn31gtsOJteY9i-G7X9tRwuAosSv2UOlhAR5CoeC_H1-U&d=oMbJSBbaPIxa%2BWjmUQq06TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=87cf6263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00005%2F1541822235852%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3nKg581IwT1jZn31gtsOJteY9i-G7X9tRwuAosSv2UOlhAR5CoeC_H1-U&h=4bc51dc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00005/1541822235852?fbclid=IwAR3nKg581IwT1jZn31gtsOJteY9i-G7X9tRwuAosSv2UOlhAR5CoeC_H1-U</a>"},{"pid":"32d55d4179e1b6c1ea7559d475580eb063dabd63","tid":896903,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"死神來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc114d5f78c5c4c76c9be52437cef725fa98ada1","tid":896903,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32d55d4179e1b6c1ea7559d475580eb063dabd63","tid":896903,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"死神來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"所以美國人先拍得出呢套戲"},{"pid":"9fee1f3edd60349733951c88391a262e721f8a62","tid":896903,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"禁酒令時期試過啦，死仲多人"}]}